{"pageProps":{"title":"Comet land guide","subtitle":"how to start","category":"Guide","date":"2022-03-26","content":"<p><a href=\"https://lgtm.com/projects/g/hyesungoh/comet-land/alerts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/lgtm/alerts/g/hyesungoh/comet-land.svg?logo=lgtm&#x26;logoWidth=18\" alt=\"Total alerts\"></a> <a href=\"https://lgtm.com/projects/g/hyesungoh/comet-land/context:javascript\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/lgtm/grade/javascript/g/hyesungoh/comet-land.svg?logo=lgtm&#x26;logoWidth=18\" alt=\"Language grade: JavaScript\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/comet-land/actions/workflows/CI.yml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/comet-land/actions/workflows/CI.yml/badge.svg\" alt=\"Continious Intergration\"></a> <a href=\"https://codecov.io/gh/hyesungoh/comet-land\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><img src=\"https://codecov.io/gh/hyesungoh/comet-land/branch/main/graph/badge.svg?token=TA7LT3RQ1P\" alt=\"codecov\"></a> <a href=\"https://dashboard.cypress.io/projects/yiddyz/runs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://dashboard.cypress.io/badge/simple/yiddyz&#x26;style=flat&#x26;logo=cypress\" alt=\"blog\"></a> <a href=\"https://dashboard.cypress.io/projects/inc4yo/runs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://dashboard.cypress.io/badge/simple/inc4yo&#x26;style=flat&#x26;logo=cypress\" alt=\"resume\"></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/159371599-95b2acd5-e5eb-482c-9ead-d8f601f034b5.png\" alt=\"comet-land-blog\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"blog-demo\"><a href=\"https://comet-land-blog.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">BLOG DEMO</a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/160653172-c56a3b64-dfa9-4708-bf95-fca2fff47964.png\" alt=\"comet-land-resume\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"resume-demo\"><a href=\"https://comet-land-resume.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">RESUME DEMO</a></h3>\n<p>Blog and Resume template with turborepo</p>\n<p>í•œêµ­ì–´ ë¬¸ì„œëŠ” <a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/hyesungoh-land/tree/main/_docs/ko-readme.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">ë‹¤ìŒ ë§í¬</a>ì—ì„œ í™•ì¸í•˜ì‹¤ ìˆ˜ ìˆìŠµë‹ˆë‹¤.</p>\n<h2 id=\"blog-feature\" class=\"heading\">Blog Feature</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/159372336-e42c1a9c-9915-4d05-9e51-4882d681dc80.gif\" alt=\"postGif\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>ğŸ‘” Code highlight with line-highlight, line-numbers</li>\n<li>ğŸ¨ Design with <a href=\"https://nextui.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">NextUI</a></li>\n<li>ğŸ½ Table of contents</li>\n<li>ğŸ© Dark mode</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/159372344-d628b817-d7f5-4322-813e-3468a62e79d6.gif\" alt=\"kbarGif\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>âŒ¨ï¸ Search with <a href=\"https://kbar.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">KBar</a></li>\n<li>ğŸ”¨ Configurable</li>\n<li>ğŸ”Š <a href=\"https://utteranc.es/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">Utterances</a> Comment</li>\n<li>ğŸ”­ Google Analytics</li>\n<li>ğŸ”¥ Hotjar</li>\n<li>ğŸ„ Lighthouse score</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/161536154-b85caf9f-0f73-4224-a1e7-540723916ff7.gif\" alt=\"blog lighthouse score\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"resume-feature\" class=\"heading\">Resume Feature</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>ğŸ¨ Design with <a href=\"https://nextui.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">NextUI</a></li>\n<li>ğŸ© Dark mode</li>\n<li>âŒ¨ï¸ Contact with <a href=\"https://kbar.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">KBar</a></li>\n<li>ğŸ”¨ Configurable</li>\n<li>ğŸ”­ Google Analytics</li>\n<li>ğŸ”¥ Hotjar</li>\n<li>ğŸ„ Lighthouse score</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/161536162-63278484-ca52-42ed-89d4-951cd31e42c1.gif\" alt=\"resume lighthouse score\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-start\" class=\"heading\">How to start</h2>\n<p><code>comet-land</code> has own generate package <a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/create-comet-land\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\"><code>create-comet-land</code></a></p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\">npx create-comet-land\n</span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token comment\"># or</span>\n</span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> create comet-land\n</span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Or using Fork or clone this repo</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>Install dependencies</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span>\n</span></code></pre>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Start Turbo !</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> turbo run dev\n</span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token comment\"># or just</span>\n</span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> dev\n</span></code></pre>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Now you can see blog at <code>localhost:3000</code>, resume at <code>localhost:3001</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-configuration\" class=\"heading\">How to configuration</h2>\n<p>Please see <code>packages/core/constants</code> directory.</p>\n<p>and you can reconfigure at that directory's variable</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Analytics directory\n<ul>\n<li>GA ID</li>\n<li>Hotjar ID</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Colors directory\n<ul>\n<li>color schema</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>General directory\n<ul>\n<li>author image</li>\n<li>default open-graph image</li>\n<li>favicon</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>SocialMedia directory\n<ul>\n<li>github</li>\n<li>instagram</li>\n<li>facebook</li>\n<li>linkedin</li>\n<li>twitter</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>and please check <code>apps/blog/_config/index.json</code> and <code>apps/resume/_config/index.json</code>.</p>\n<p>This files are placing each app's configuration variable.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use-it\" class=\"heading\">How to use it</h2>\n<p>please read following link.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/hyesungoh-land/tree/main/_docs/en-blog.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">how to add blog post</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/hyesungoh-land/tree/main/_docs/en-resume.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">how to custom resume</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-deploy-with-vercel\" class=\"heading\">How to deploy with vercel</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-import-git-repository\">1. Import git repository</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/177278351-7b82fcbe-e6db-46bd-93f4-10e8524ef2bf.gif\" alt=\"deploy step 1\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-select-framework-preset-to-nextjs\">2. Select framework preset to <code>Next.js</code></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/177278363-509b3d69-f692-4458-8bc2-62173eef5e7e.gif\" alt=\"deploy step 2\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-set-root-directory-to-appsblog-or-appsresume\">3. Set root directory to <code>apps/blog</code> or <code>apps/resume</code></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/177278370-1651b4d7-e561-44df-8a62-a283450773d9.gif\" alt=\"deploy step 3\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"4-set-build-command\">4. Set build command</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/177278380-659ba348-7952-4875-9e19-0a006ad57c1a.gif\" alt=\"deploy step 4\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>blog build command</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>/<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;&#x26;</span> npx turbo run build --scope<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>blog --include-dependencies --no-deps\n</span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>resume build command</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>/<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;&#x26;</span> npx turbo run build --scope<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>resume --include-dependencies --no-deps\n</span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"5-click-the-deploy-button-\">5. Click the Deploy button! ğŸ‰</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26461307/177278617-82982395-d1fc-46f1-8f96-f7cb7bae95d9.png\" alt=\"click the deploy button\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"more-information\">More information</h3>\n<p>This project using <code>turborepo</code>.</p>\n<p>so, you can find more information at this <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/concepts/monorepos/turborepo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">vercel guide</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-add-more-packages\" class=\"heading\">How to add more packages</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>scope packages</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> where-you-want\n</span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> package-name\n</span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>global packages</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> package-name -W\n</span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>global dev packages</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash code-highlight\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> package-name -DW\n</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"trouble-shootings\" class=\"heading\">Trouble shootings</h2>\n<p>check <a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/comet-land/wiki/Trouble-Shooting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">this wiki</a> please! it might be help</p>\n<h2 id=\"use-case\" class=\"heading\">Use Case</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hyesungoh/hyesungoh.xyz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">hyesungoh.xyz</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"inspired\" class=\"heading\">Inspired</h2>\n<p>I inspired below blogs and resume.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://overreacted.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">Overreacted</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://yceffort.kr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">Yceffort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">gatsby-starter-bee</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vallista.kr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">vallista-land</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hyunseob.github.io/resume/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferer\">hyunseob.github.io/resume</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"license\" class=\"heading\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT</p>","ogImage":"https://img.shields.io/lgtm/alerts/g/hyesungoh/comet-land.svg?logo=lgtm&#x26;logoWidth=18"},"__N_SSG":true}